      <span class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 addtoany_list" data-a2a-url="https://worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/fiction/critical-lovemaking-mika-seifert" data-a2a-title="Critical Lovemaking, by Mika Seifert"><a class="a2a_button_facebook"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter"></a><a class="a2a_button_email"></a><a class="a2a_dd addtoany_share" href="https://www.addtoany.com/share#url=https%3A%2F%2Fworldliteraturetoday.org%2Fblog%2Ffiction%2Fcritical-lovemaking-mika-seifert&amp;title=Critical%20Lovemaking%2C%20by%20Mika%20Seifert"></a></span>

    
