                                  Photo: Katja Pfeifer
                                </div>
                                                          </div>
                                                                                            <p style="margin-bottom:12.0pt;"><a href="https://mikaseifert.com/index.html"><strong>Mika Seifert</strong></a> is a writer, concert violinist, and broker of rare violin bows. His short stories have been published in the <em>Antioch Review</em>, <em>Chicago Review</em>, <em>Image Journal</em>, <em>London Magazine</em>, <em>Missouri Review</em>, <em>Southern Review</em>, and elsewhere.</p>
